source:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_00<tab>Muna Vanu needs a skilled hand to attend to a difficult task.
※The difficulty of this quest will be synced to your current level.
target:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト受注クラス・ジョブ制限<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
ナッキ島のムナバヌは、人手不足に悩んでいるようだ。

source:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_01<tab>Muna Vanu has need of a strong, energetic paissa, but due to his responsibilities to the tribe, he has not the time to undertake the drawn-out task of capturing such wily prey himself. Furnishing you with a large sack in which to hold the beast, he bids you travel westward to where these creatures are most plentiful. They can be caught by digging a hole, which the careless creatures will fall into, finding themselves stuck.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_01<tab>※本クエストには
「<var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var><var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> レベルアジャスト受注クラス・ジョブ制限」が、
　設定されています。
　受注時と同じクラス・ジョブでのみ進行できます。

ムナバヌから、罠を使ってパイッサを捕まえるように依頼された。オク・グンド西の「<var 28 ((EObj)) F61E9EA601 /var>」に落とし穴を掘ろう。

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_02<tab>You dig a hole, deep and wide enough to trap the sturdiest of paissas. Now you must wait for just such a beast to fall for this obvious─but apparently effective─ploy.
target: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_02<tab>落とし穴を掘った。オク・グンド西の「<var 28 ((EObj)) F61E9EAB01 /var>」で待機しよう。

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_03<tab>It's not long before a spry but oblivious paissa falls straight into the hole you dug. Put the creature into the sack the Vanu gave you before it escapes.
target: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_03<tab>冒険者が掘った落とし穴に、パイッサが嵌ったようだ。落とし穴に嵌った「活きのいいパイッサ」に「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8C0F01 /var>」を使って捕獲しよう。

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_04<tab>The paissa puts up little resistance as you extricate it from the hole and place it in the sack. Return your prize to Muna Vanu.
target: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_04<tab><var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8C0301 /var>を入手した。ナッキ島の「ムナバヌ」に「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8C0301 /var>」を渡そう。

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_05<tab>Muna Vanu explains that he has been challenged by a friend from the Zundu tribe to a paissafight. Though his tribe owes theirs a great debt, the elderly Vanu cannot bring dishonor on his people by losing the fight. Once properly trained, the spry and stalwart creature you captured should help secure his victory in the upcoming challenge.
target: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_SEQ_05<tab>ムナバヌに、<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8C0301 /var>を渡した。バヌバヌ族の間で行われる「闘パイッサ」という競技で勝つため、捕らえたパイッサを鍛え上げるつもりのようだ。

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_TODO_00<tab>Dig a hole at the specified location.
target: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_TODO_00<tab><var 28 ((EObj)) F61E9EA601 /var>に落とし穴を掘る

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_TODO_01<tab>Lie in wait until a paissa falls for the trap.

target: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_TODO_02<tab>活きのいいパイッサに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8C0F01 /var>を使って捕獲

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_TODO_03<tab>Deliver the captured paissa to Muna Vanu.
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_001<tab>Hmmm... But who is skilled enough to... Oh, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> arrives at perfect moment!
target:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_001<tab>ぐぬぬ、ぐぬぬ……どうしたものか……。
ハッ、<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>さま！
これ以上ない時に、声をかけてくださいましたね！

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_002<tab>Muna Vanu has need of paissa─lively one, full of spirit. But catching paissa takes time, and I have responsibilities to tribe and cannot spare such time.
target:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_002<tab>どうしても「活きのいいパイッサ」が必要なのです。
ですが、成さねばならぬ村の仕事が山積みでして……
罠をしかけに行くこともできません。

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_003<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, please catch paissa for Muna Vanu. Best way is to dig hole. Paissa falls right into hole and cannot get out. Many paissas roam west of Ok' Gundu. Hunt there, and catch prey alive in this sack.
target:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_003<tab>どうか、どうか、<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>さま。
「オク・グンド」西方に落とし穴を掘り、
掛かった「活きのいいパイッサ」を、この袋で捕らえてください！

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_SYSTEM_000_040<tab>You slip the struggling paissa into the sack.
target: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_SYSTEM_000_040<tab>落とし穴に嵌っている「活きのいいパイッサ」を捕まえた！

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_050<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> returns! Does <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> catch fit and sprightly paissa?
target:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_050<tab>ハッ、<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>さま！
それで、それで、パイッサ狩りはいかがでしたか？

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_051<tab>Yes! Yes! Many thanks! Fluffy like summer storm cloud, sprightly like zephyr wind. Muna Vanu wins for certain now, cannot lose with this perfect paissa!
target:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_051<tab>なんと、なんと、素晴らしい！
積乱雲のように力強く、雄々しいパイッサではありませんか！
これならば勝てる、必ず勝てますぞ！

source: TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_052<tab>Ah... Perhaps Muna Vanu gets carried away. Friend from Ok' Zundu lays challenge in paissafight, and to lose brings shame to all Gundu!
target:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_052<tab>ハッ……私としたことが興奮してしまいました。
実は「大らかなズンド」の友人と、部族の名誉を懸けて、
「闘パイッサ」で勝負することになっておりましてな。

source:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_053<tab>Although we owe Zundu great debt, we cannot let them win. Honor of whole tribe depends on fight! I train this paissa to defeat Zundu paissa─
without mercy.
target:
TEXT_BANVAN504_02196_02196_MUNAVANU_000_053<tab>私たちを助けてくれた恩人が相手とはいえ、
神聖なる「闘パイッサ」となれば、決して手を抜けません。
このパイッサを鍛え上げ、必ずや勝利を手にして見せますぞ！
